dct_description_sm: Includes inset map of Gavdos (island) and Gavdopoula (islet). Map shows six classes of roads; historical sites; monasteries. Verso shows map with seven hiking destinations in Crete; each hiking destination accompanied by map, photograph, written description (in parallel Greek and English), and advertisement for map available for purchase from publisher "Anavasi."
